name: Shot by Rhythm
description: This piece is a digital art that i created as part of my fine art photography project 'Dance Like It's Renaissance'. I'm working on this project since 2019. I've done series of photoshoots with dancers around the world. The project aims to study the emotions of motion in an aesthetic way trough dance art. I've collaborated dance artist in Florida, Costa Rica, Turkey so far to complete the first phase of the project. I'm very excited to drop this piece as part of #henthousand challenge.
